# Cloudflare API Token with Tunnel:Edit and DNS:Edit permissions
# Get this from https://dash.cloudflare.com/profile/api-tokens
# Create a token with:
# - Permissions: Zone:Zone:Read, Zone:DNS:Edit, Account:Cloudflare Tunnel:Edit
# - Zone Resources: Include - All zones (or specific zone)
# - Account Resources: Include - All accounts (or specific account)
CLOUDFLARE_API_KEY=your-cloudflare-api-token-here

# Optional: Uncomment and set these if you have multiple accounts/zones
# CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=your-account-id
# CLOUDFLARE_ZONE_ID=your-zone-id